OL,3,C'Rot in hell!': Court erupts as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murdering ex's partner
OL,6,FA family has screamed in court as a
OL,7,Fman was jailed for life for
OL,8,F'torturing' his ex-girlfriend's new
OL,9,Fpartner to death.
OL,11,FJohn Belfield, 31, was sentenced to a
OL,12,Fminimum term of 37 years on Thursday 4
OL,13,FJuly, after he was convicted of
OL,14,Fmurdering Thomas Campbell on 3 July
OL,15,F2022.
OL,17,FAfter sentencing, as he was led to the
OL,18,Fcells, cries of "rot in hell" could be
OL,19,Fheard.
