OL,3,C'Rot in hell!': Court erupts as man
OL,4,Cjailed for murdering ex's partner
OL,6,FManchester Crown Court heard how
OL,7,FBelfield recruited a team to help him
OL,8,Fkill Thomas Campbell in Tameside after
OL,9,Fhe began a relationship with Demi-Lee
OL,10,FDriver, his killer's ex-partner.
OL,12,FBelfield was one of three men who lay
OL,13,Fin wait as Campbell arrived home late
OL,14,Fon a Saturday night on July 2, 2022.
OL,16,FThe court heard the killing followed a
OL,17,Fweek of hostile surveillance carried
OL,18,Fout on 38-year-old Mr Campbell by
OL,19,FBelfield and his conspirators.
