OL,6,FWhen they struck, Campbell could be
OL,7,Fheard to scream as the trio attacked
OL,8,Fand subdued him on his front drive,
OL,9,Fbefore bundling him inside the house
OL,10,Fon Riverside in Mossley, Tameside.
OL,12,FOver two hours he was stabbed,
OL,13,Fstrangled and had hot liquid poured on
OL,14,Fhis genitals. Prosecutors said he was
OL,15,F"tortured to death", having suffered
OL,16,F61 separate injuries.
OL,18,FA huge murder investigation was
OL,19,Flaunched, and Belfield's conviction is
OL,20,Fthe fourth related to Thomas
OL,21,FCampbell's death.
