OL,6,FThe 31-year-old initially escaped
OL,7,Fjustice by fleeing to Suriname, a
OL,8,Fsmall South American nation north of
OL,9,FBrazil. He was eventually arrested by
OL,10,Flocal police on drug charges, and
OL,11,Fserved some time in prison before
OL,12,FSuriname and Dutch authorities brought
OL,13,Fhim back to Manchester to face justice
OL,14,Ffor the murder of Mr Campbell.
OL,16,FDuring that time three others were
OL,17,Fconvicted in connection with Mr
OL,18,FCampbell's murder, including his ex-
OL,19,Fwife.
