OL,6,FReece Steven, who Belfield recruited
OL,7,Finto the crime, and was one of the
OL,8,Fthree attackers to kill Thomas
OL,9,FCampbell, was also found guilty of
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FStephen Cleworth, who Belfield also
OL,13,Frecruited, planted the tracking device
OL,14,Fon Campbell's car, was convicted of
OL,15,Fmanslaughter.
